正式宣布将邀请哪些国家参加G7峰会。但据路透社报道，意大利计划邀请突尼斯、肯尼亚、阿尔及利亚、南非等国，还邀请印度、巴西和阿根廷等“非洲和地中海以外”国家，而这与韩国总统室的解释不符合。 报道提及，G7由美国、英国、法国、德国、意大利、加拿大、日本七个成员国组成，每年的轮值主席国有权邀请非成员国参会。韩国自2020年后共三次受邀参与G7峰会，前总统文在寅在2020年、2021年分别受美国和英国邀请参会，尹锡悦去年应日方邀请参会。 韩国两次没有受到邀请参加G7峰会，都是在尹锡悦担任总统期间。除今年外，2022年德国担任G7轮值主席国时，没有邀请韩国。当时，韩国一名外交人士告诉《朝鲜日报》：“据我了解，政府调动了所有外交资源，让尹总统出席G7，但最终没有获得邀请。”韩国被G7峰会排除在外，韩反对党：只重视与美日关系的后果"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ikra7icmfmOMtEAMaCTEwNzU0ODQ1OCDA75axBjAAOB9ABnIJNjUzNzE3OTg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"98 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-0bfaa32906338093594a665378e21b4a_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1713759522.745556","card_id":"Q_653654592","target":{"id":653654592,"title":"为什么看书之后看透了很多事?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/653654592","type":"question","created":1713694649,"answer_count":101,"follower_count":192,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[113,5425,49916,84670,138771],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAIkra7icmfmOMtEAMaCTEwNzUzNDQ0NyC5z5OxBjAAOMABQAdyCTY1MzY1NDU5MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"90 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-e0f0aa0baf4df67f4a4292c751cd9e03_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1713759522.745888","card_id":"Q_653683569","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":653683569,"title":"23-24 赛季西甲皇家马德里 3:2 巴塞罗那，如何评价这场比赛？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/653683569","type":"question","created":1713726229,"answer_count":11,"follower_count":11,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"